Summary: 2 bright lights moving in an usual fashion.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was going for a night time walk and I usually look up at the stars on clear nights. This night, something caught my attention steaking across the sky. It was approx about 3 miles away and very high up in the air. I noticed the object was zig zagging up and down and accelerating at a high rate of speed. It didnt seem to be in any type of order or pattern. I grabbed my cell phone that has a 1.3 megapixal camera. The object was 2 light conjoined on one object. I have enclosed 2 pics of 2 different objects on 2 different nights that very similar but were moving in different fashions 3 months apart.
